<topic template="Default" status="Needs Review" modified="2026-04-08T09:42:34.517Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>7.4 Enabling BTS in Tool Management</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading3">在工具管理中启用 BTS</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">需要进行 BT 检查的工具需要在工具管理屏幕中注册。这样，在将刀具送回刀库时，首先要进行 BT 检查，如果没有破损刀具，则会取回新刀具。如果发现刀具破损，则发出警报并终止刀具更换周期。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">登记需要或不需要 BTS 检查的步骤</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:10px;">导航至工具数据屏幕</para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[CSTM/GRPH]</text>。显示牧野自定义屏幕主菜单屏幕。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:24px;"><image src="Makino Custom Screen.png" scale="40.00%" width="320" height="240" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><anchor id="Fig7.4" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER3=7%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160; 主菜单屏幕</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">选择<text style="font-weight:bold;">[设置]</text>&#32;<text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text>&#32;<text style="font-weight:bold;">[工具数据]</text>&#32;<text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">®</text>按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[选择]</text>软键。显示 &quot;工具管理（列表）&quot; 屏幕。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:14px; margin-left:24px;"><image src="7. Tool management List Screen - 1.png" scale="40.00%" width="320" height="240" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><anchor id="Fig7.5" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER3=7%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160; 工具管理（列表）屏幕</text></para>
    <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:19px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:19px; margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">按 </text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">[细节]</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> 软键。显示 &quot;工具管理（细节）&quot;屏幕。</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:19px; margin-left:24px;"><image src="7. Tool management Detail Screen.png" scale="40.00%" width="320" height="240" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:center; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:16px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:159px left ;"><anchor id="Fig7.6" styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;"></anchor><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:11pt;">图 &lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER3=7%&gt;.&lt;%HMFIGURECOUNTER%&gt; &#160; 工具管理（细节）屏幕</text></para>
    <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">使用 <text style="font-weight:bold;">[上一页]</text>/<text style="font-weight:bold;">[向下翻页] </text>键向下滚动刀库中的刀具。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">对于需要 BT 检查的刀具，在<text style="font-weight:bold;">BTS 长度</text>字段中输入刀具长度，并在<text style="font-weight:bold;">BT 检查</text>字段中将<text style="font-weight:bold;">BT</text>检查设为 &quot;是&quot;。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-left:24px;">上述步骤将使已注册的刀具进入 BT 检查流程。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-left:24px; page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
